cs.CR, cs.SE, cs.PL, cs.AI, cs.SI 

The paper discusses the issue of malware detection in mobile platforms, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The proposed approach involves program analysis, which is a common topic in software engineering (cs.SE) and programming languages (cs.PL). The use of semantic predicates and human judgment also suggests the involvement of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and possibly social and information networks (cs.SI) in the analysis process.
